Name: Strawberry Shortcake Mount
Desc:
[Master Level: 1]
You can travel at a significant speed on a strawberry shortcake, which enables double-jump.

Desc.Old:
[Master Level: 1]
You can travel at a significant speed on a strawberry shortcake, which enables double-jump. Double-click your destination on the World Map and you will fly automatically toward it along the navigation route. (Auto flight is available only on certain continents, including Victoria Island. You can expand your Smart Mount-permitted continents by buying Flight Permits from Instructor Irvine.)
